text: I went in the afternoon to have a late lunch & pay some bills. Wonderfully quiet & my pizza came very fast & it was so good...double cheese & mushroom & the mushrooms were the canned ones which is what I like on a pizza. Did I say it was so good,  it truly was! Definitely going back! Thanks Jamie for the great service!
